</sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-FSAAPPruthi_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-FSAAPPruthi_3-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fsa.gov.uk/pages/consumerinformation/firmnews/2010/anderson_peacock_pruthi.shtml\">\"Anderson, Peacock and Pruthi to pay \u00a3115m after unlawfully accepting deposits\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Financial_Services_Authority\" title=\"Financial Services Authority\">Financial Services Authority</a>. 29 March 2011<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2102-03-08</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Anderson%2C+Peacock+and+Pruthi+to+pay+%C2%A3115m+after+unlawfully+accepting+deposits&amp;rft.pub=Financial+Services+Authority&amp;rft.date=2011-03-29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fsa.gov.uk%2Fpages%2Fconsumerinformation%2Ffirmnews%2F2010%2Fanderson_peacock_pruthi.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABusiness+Consulting+International\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:100%\" class=\"error citation-comment\">Check date values in: <code style=\"color:inherit; border:inherit; padding:inherit;\">&#124;accessdate=</code> (<a href=\"/wiki/Help:CS1_errors#bad_date\" title=\"Help:CS1 errors\">help</a>)</span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://news.sky.com/skynews/article/0,,30100-1311171,00.html\">Farnborough Air Crash: Cessna Aircraft Goes Down In Kent |Sky News|UK News</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.planetlemans.com/2008/03/30/david-leslie-and-richard-lloyd-killed-in-plane-accident/\">\"David Leslie and Richard Lloyd killed in plane accident\"</a>. Planetlemans. 30 March 2008<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2008-03-30</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=David+Leslie+and+Richard+Lloyd+killed+in+plane+accident&amp;rft.pub=Planetlemans&amp;rft.date=2008-03-30&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.planetlemans.com%2F2008%2F03%2F30%2Fdavid-leslie-and-richard-lloyd-killed-in-plane-accident%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABusiness+Consulting+International\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fsa.gov.uk/consumerinformation/firmnews/2011/anderson_peacock_pruthi.shtml\">\"Call to clients of Anderson, Peacock and Pruthi\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Financial_Services_Authority\" title=\"Financial Services Authority\">Financial Services Authority</a>. 29 March 2011<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2102-03-08</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Call+to+clients+of+Anderson%2C+Peacock+and+Pruthi&amp;rft.pub=Financial+Services+Authority&amp;rft.date=2011-03-29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fsa.gov.uk%2Fconsumerinformation%2Ffirmnews%2F2011%2Fanderson_peacock_pruthi.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABusiness+Consulting+International\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:100%\" class=\"error citati